%e A212662 k=39, x=4, y=35 and 39=4+35; k'=16, x'=4, y'=12 and 16=4+12;
%e A212662 k=39, x=13, y=26 and 39=13+26; k'=16, x'=1, y'=15 and 16=1+15.
